data.title: B Site Off-Angle Top Box Rendezvous
data.description: Use this simple, but powerful off-angle to catch players aggressively scouting the B Site. You can also set your Rendezvous further back towards spawn, to prevent a fast pop.

data.title: Top Market Rendezvous
data.description: This Rendezvous setup gives you height to allow you to cover Market and B Main.

data.title: Aggressive A Main TP to Site
data.description: Use this Rendezvous setup to allow you to play aggressively off of A Main.
